name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Italy Roads, Insular Italy, 2008
description: This Dataset is part of five datasets downloaded from the openstreetmap, Geofabrik website and includes information and locations of roads throughout insular Italy. The dataset includes Road names and type. Type of road includes information on whether the road is a primary, residential or secondary road, etc. Because the dataset for the entire country was too big, it was divided into north western, north eastern,central, southern and insular Italy.
